data.description: This Cape Cod home has endless potential. The first floor consist of a family room with wood flooring, eat in kitchen, two bedrooms, and a full bathroom. There is one additional large bedroom on the second level. The roof was installed in 2014. The windows were replaced in 2014. New a/c unit in 2015. Basement glass block windows installed in 2019. Exterior doors installed in 2022. Interior doors replaced in 2023. Located in the Boardman School District and is ready for a new homeowner.
